  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicentre, randomised, placebo-controlled, double-blind, three-arm parallel,
      Phase IIa study to evaluate the efficacy, safety and tolerability of MIV-711 in patients with
      knee osteoarthritis (OA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
